# ─── Personal content (the whole point of this repo is the framework, not your content) ───

# Raw source materials
raw/*
!raw/README.md
!raw/.gitkeep

# Atoms — all topic-branches and their contents are yours, not for the public repo
atoms/*
!atoms/README.md
!atoms/_template.md
!atoms/.gitkeep

# Compiled wiki pages
wiki/*
!wiki/_template.md
!wiki/.gitkeep

# Auto-generated artifacts
index.md
log.md
lint-report.md

# Personal notes / analysis (not for the public repo)
GAP-ANALYSIS.md

